	* nnimap.el (nnimap-retrieve-headers-from-server): Fix last change.

2005-03-10  Arne Jørgensen  <arne@arnested.dk>  (tiny change)

	* nnimap.el (nnimap-retrieve-headers-from-server): Fix off-by-one flaw.

